/// It styles them with a style that conforms to the
/// <a href="https://maplibre.org/maplibre-style-spec/">MapLibre Style Spec</a>.
/// Such styles can be designed with
/// <a href="https://maplibre.org/maputnik/">Maputnik</a>.
